    • Method Detail

      • getContracts

        ContractEntity getContracts(java.lang.String country)
        Lists the contracts of a given partner. Allows filtering by country. Synchronous execution.
        Parameters:
        country - ISO 3166 alpha 3 country code (e.g. CIV, see https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-1). If null no filtering.
        Returns:
        object containing information about your SMS balance and the expiration date
        See Also:
        https://www.orangepartner.com/content/getting-started-sms?api=sms_ci_product#getcontracts

      • getContracts

        void getContracts(java.lang.String country,
                  <any> callback)
        Lists the contracts of a given partner. Allows filtering by country. Asynchronous execution.
        Parameters:
        country - ISO 3166 alpha 3 country code (e.g. CIV, see https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-1). If null no filtering.
        callback - Communicates the response from the server. If the request was successful, the response will be a ContractEntity object (accessible from success method). Otherwise an error object (accessible from failure method).
        See Also:
        https://www.orangepartner.com/content/getting-started-sms?api=sms_ci_product#getcontracts
